snippet.textDisplay:
ku ja = kaha
en ja = yaha
un ja = udhar
mann = me/ mein
un = woh
Enn = yeh / ye
tu = tum
tu kuja bodi = tum kahan the?
mann Dar iran Bodam = me iran me tha
unn/oon kuja bod= woh kahan the
unn En'ja Bod = woh yahaan the.
hast = Hai.
Esmet Chi Hast/ Chi'ay? = apka Naam kia hai
🤐
Persian/ Farsi is beautiful language just Like our Beautiful Urdu. :) without Persian and Arabic Urdu would be just Hindi :(

if you still don't appreciate Farsi/ Persian in Urdu then just listen and read Pakistani National Anthem again.
